headline: Molson Coors Q1 Earnings to Reflect Positive Trends: Time to Buy?
summary: TAP's Q1 results are expected to reflect gains from strong brand resilience, volume growth and expanded market share, offset by a tough macroeconomic environment.

headline: Gear Up for Molson Coors (TAP) Q1 Earnings: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Besides Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimates for Molson Coors (TAP), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended March 2025.
